data.description: Assumable 2.75% VA loan. Check the current interest rates then see what a magnificent opportunity this can be for the right buyer.  Call helpful lister for more info. ** Shipley Homestead** Gorgeous upscale townhome in sought after community features elegant brick front with stone details and a spacious, open floor plan to die for! This 3-level home offers a 2 car garage + parking pad and Basement Level that is fully finished with entertaining Family Room with NEW luxury vinyl plank flooring, built-in TV console, lots of windows and ground level walk-out to privacy fenced yard. The Main Level explodes with open space with hardwood on the entire level and offers  a huge, stylish center Island, stainless steel appliances, gas cooking and eating area with front box bay window and rear living room with walk door to a wonderful 21 x 21 Deck with composite flooring and  vinyl railings. The Upper Level offers a luxurious Primary Bedroom with a 9x6 walk-in closet, attached Primary Bath with double sinks, sunken tub and separate shower with glass doors. Bedrooms 2 & 3 are bright and sunny with great closet space. This home is turn-key ready with new paint, shampooed carpets and has been professionally cleaned.  The neighbored is just a few minutes away from NSA/Ft. Meade main gate, B/W Parkway, Rt. 32 and Arundel Mills Mall. The HOA is low at $120 per month and includes an outdoor pool, fitness center, playground and dog park. Add this home to your list to see and you will not be disappointed!
